""Bill"" Irvine Special Collection Photo Guam Additional Information: B-29 Boeing aircraft in formation over Guam in World War II, Brigadier General Clarence Irvine enjoyed a long distinguished military career, mainly involving engineering. He served with the XXI Bomber Command (B-29's) during WWII and continued to serve throughout the 1950s and 1960s. Corporation Name: Boeing Tags: Brigadier General Clarence S.
